title: The Yoke Destroyer | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: The Yoke Destroyer | Joel Osteen
description:
A yoke is anything that is holding you back from your full potential. The good news is, our God is the yoke destroyer. He can remove anything that's keeping you from becoming who God created you to be.


Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
